Company Overview
It gives us great pleasure to introduce our esteemed agency, Geo Sphere Recruitment Philippines, Inc.(GSRP). GSRPI is a Filipino owned corporation, duly registered with the Securities and Exchange Commission and duly licensed by the Philippine Overseas Employment Administration (POEA). Our main offices are housed in the JBC Clarion Building; owned by our President - CEO Benjamin S. Talan, and located along the main thoroughfare of Marikina City, an emerging hub for the business outsourcing industry. GSRPI’s managers and officers have been in the recruitment business for over 20 years, holding executive, managerial and marketing positions in their previous agencies. We are proud of their impeccable track records: excellent standing with the POEA and the industry. In view of our past experiences, we are confident that we can meet our Clients/Principals expectations and supply their Filipino manpower requirements at any given time.
